snippet.textDisplay: Assam has always been very important to me I've so many memories from there I only lived there for 3 years but the experience I got, things I learnt are going to remain with me for a lifetime and Coke Studio, I thank you for representing Assam's music heritage on a global stage Despite being from Bihar I love Assam more than Bihar, I feel so overwhelmed upon seeing that finally, Assam is getting recognition it deserved.
